<!doctype html>
<html class="no-js" lang="en" dir="ltr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Coding | Plinth'17</title>
        <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/8720ae4a19.js"></script>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
      <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/foundation/6.2.3/foundation.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/competitions.css" />
    </head>
    <body>

        <% include partials/header %>
        <%if (!isLoggedIn) { %>
                <% include partials/reg-form %>
        <% } %>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="row head">
                <div class="small-10 small-centered columns text-center">
                    <h4>Coding</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row desc">
                <div class="small-12 columns text-center">
                    <p>Setting apart all the creativities, imaginations or logistics ; coders are the ones who can storm off their brains and come up with a new solution to each problem that exists. So join us to be the warrior of codes and unleash your skills in the battle field.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="big-wrapper">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="large-8 large-centered small-10 small-centered columns">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 small-centered medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                                <img src="media/icons/coding/fix_the_bug.svg" class="event-main-page-image" />
                                <div class="container">
                                    <p class="name">Fix the Bug</p>
                                    <p class="name-desc">Can  you spot a bug the way eagle spots a mouse?</p>
                                </div>
                                <a href="/competitions/coding/fix_the_bug" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 small-centered medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                              <img src="media/icons/coding/iupc.svg" class="event-main-page-image" />
                              <div class="container">
                                <p class="name">IUPC</p>
                                <p class="name-desc">See logic in everything around? Is your daily grammar a 'SYNTAX'? </p>
                              </div>
                              <a href="/competitions/coding/iupc" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="small-10 medium-4 large-4 end small-offset-1 medium-uncentered columns">
                            <div class="card text-center">
                              <img src="media/icons/coding/iupc_distraction.svg"  class="event-main-page-image" />
                              <div class="container">
                                  <p class="name">IUPC Distraction</p>
                                  <p class="name-desc">You can code alright.But CAN you code while being distracted?</p>
                              </div>
                              <a href="/competitions/coding/iupc_distraction" class="know-more">Know More ></a>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <% include partials/footer %>

    </body>
</html>
